     --radius-full: 9999px;
     ```

   - **`/home/jwilger/projects/todo_list/templates/base.html`**
     - The Askama base template that all pages extend
     - I reviewed and design-approved this template
     ```html
     <!DOCTYPE html>
     <html lang="en">
     <head>
         <meta charset="UTF-8">
         <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
         <title>{% block title %}Todo List{% endblock %}</title>
