     ```

   - **`/home/jwilger/projects/todo_list/templates/register.html`** (from earlier Luca build, now lost/rebuilt)
     - Registration form template I reviewed and provided 6 design issues on
     - Issues: no component CSS, class name mismatch, missing form wrapper (24rem), missing spacing, unstyled footer text, heading text ("Create an account" should be "Create your account")

   - **`/home/jwilger/projects/todo_list/docs/user-stories.md`**
     - Read for design alignment -- 8 user stories (US-1 through US-8) with acceptance criteria
     - Key design implications: password confirmation field, generic error messages for security, lightweight delete confirmation, edit needs both no-JS page and HTMX inline mode

   - **`/home/jwilger/projects/todo_list/.team/steve-schoger.md`** - My team profile
   - **`/home/jwilger/projects/todo_list/PROJECT.md`** - Project owner constraints
   - **`/home/jwilger/projects/todo_list/TEAM_AGREEMENTS.md`** - Team conventions (CSS layers, design token flow, Feature Workflow)

   - **Component CSS Specs** (sent to Lea, not yet in file):
     ```css
