   - **team-lead**: New commit discipline rules for team consensus (5 rules)
   - **team-lead**: STOP - push existing work before writing more
   - **kent-beck**: Final task breakdown proposal (revised simpler version folding base template into registration)
   - **marty-cagan**: Password resolved (progressive enhancement), delete timeout confirmed
   - **heydon-pickering**: Skip link and delete confirmation a11y review (focus-to-Cancel, timeout-respects-focus, aria-labels)
   - **heydon-pickering**: Token change already committed, all 4 decisions in place
